<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.7.10">
<l>aṉṉa maṉṉupaim pūmpoḻil cūḻnta vaḻuntūr mēlticai niṉṟavam māṉai</l>
<l>kaṉṉi maṉṉutiṇ ṭōḷkali kaṉṟi yāli nāṭaṉmaṅ kaikkula vēntaṉ</l>
<l>coṉṉa viṉtamiḻ naṉmaṇik kōvai tūya mālaiyi vaipattum  vallār</l>
<l>maṉṉi maṉṉava rāyula kāṇṭu māṉa veṇkuṭaik kīḻmakiḻ vārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master this pristine garland of ten [verses],</l>
<l rend="indent">this string of fine jewels in sweet Tamil,</l>
<l>Composed by Kalikaṉṟi with youthful, sturdy, strong arms,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one of Āli country, clan ruler of Maṅkai,</l>
<l>About the lord who stands at the west side of Aḻuntūr</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by verdant, flowered groves where swans linger,</l>
<l>They will rejoice under a royal, white canopy,</l>
<l rend="indent">as if ruling the world as stalwart kings.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
